{"tid":1434620,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"招識unity 同有心整香港本地game巴打","createTime":"2019-08-08T23:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T15:49:10.000Z","uid":104660,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8c7c512438b3c827ee55abece4b9b180a93a6daa","tid":1434620,"uid":104660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:40:03.000Z","msg":"小弟依家同3個人一齊合作緊整一隻3D RPG game，冇錯，個scale都幾大<br />\n所以需要人手:<br />\n暫時有<br />\n2個programmer<br />\n1個project manager<br />\n1個game designer<br />\n<br />\n需要不同既人包括:<br />\n用unity砌場景<br />\nunity programming<br />\n2D/3D 畫圖/動畫 <br />\n最好對整game或unity認識愈深愈好( 高階D例如寫shader, reflection probe應用,燈光等等)<br />\n<br />\n有興趣請聯絡小弟了解更多詳情<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/Magicasahole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FMagicasahole&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=f3550135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Magicasahole</a><br />\n<br />\n需要係有時間有heart長期做野既<br />\n每星期三會有一次online meeting<br />\n現階段我地係冇錢收的，目標係希望整個demo version 放上kickstarter睇下有冇人肯支持我地繼續開發"},{"pid":"64aaec266014670a7c76c693b49524e8baa9469d","tid":1434620,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:41:46.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6b4491645a836fe3feccf9e599f689b49d891a","tid":1434620,"uid":61667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"801d567f3cb0badce58c18a07b8ecb90047db221","tid":1434620,"uid":24613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7ea0c8f34c26b0d8bfab8984170476e2d60ee9","tid":1434620,"uid":129142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"支持本地創作 可惜我唔係呢方面嘅人才 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da40a049d311d86b8fa953e